{"tid":2140430,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"刀劍神域作者川原礫寫莉法俾豬屌係有咁嘅原因","createTime":"2020-08-05T04:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T17:22:43.000Z","uid":57911,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4472665e4c284f3d5c7632fda1b45184e06f4bd9","tid":2140430,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"就係為咗加速世界續集試水溫<br />\n要知道大家一直埋怨有田春雪唔靚仔已經對川原礫構成好大心理陰影<br />\n佢要將加速世界劇情寫入去<br />\n就係要你班人睇隻豬搞一個前集女主角<br />\n咁先符合到加速世界價值觀<br />\n川原礫最用心寫嘅故仔就係因為你班人用審美眼光歧視男豬係隻豬而踐踏咗一套優秀作品<br />\n作者要向世界控訴<br />\n就算你唔想再見到隻豬我都會逼你睇<br />\n直到更多人願意接受家畜世界佢先會收手<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/08/05/115921_5a86b9e1d2b28553193e1f8a04cbb6ba.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F08%2F05%2F115921_5a86b9e1d2b28553193e1f8a04cbb6ba.jpeg&h=a016112b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44890984c1e57848609eb836b395a1d1390fe02e","tid":2140430,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:13:34.000Z","msg":"套野真係咁撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？哩啲唔係黑獸既劇情黎咩<br />\n利申：冇睇刀劍"},{"pid":"c46e8eb32f64cb8e253d62d062c2834bec6d1bf3","tid":2140430,"uid":207149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44890984c1e57848609eb836b395a1d1390fe02e","tid":2140430,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:13:34.000Z","msg":"套野真係咁撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？哩啲唔係黑獸既劇情黎咩<br />\n利申：冇睇刀劍"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:21:32.000Z","msg":"隻豬好仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b571be11d003f27ea51337a3b71961c0d5781e9","tid":2140430,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c46e8eb32f64cb8e253d62d062c2834bec6d1bf3","tid":2140430,"uid":207149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44890984c1e5784860